## A grove on Cradle Rock where the player chops wood for Cogwise
## Godfrey's spacecraft project. Hosts the [WoodCuttingSign] launcher
## that fires the Lumberjacking puzzle. Reached via the ToForest door
## on the shore (near the Workshop).
##
## Shared movement / spawn / ESC behavior comes from [BaseLocation].
## This script stays empty for future Forest-specific logic (e.g.
## ambient SFX, daytime tint).
class_name Forest
extends BaseLocation